It needs to be renovated, updated.

52
00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:39.160
It needs new fixtures and doors and paint and things like that.

53
00:02:39.410 --> 00:02:42.700
You can say, "this place could use a renovation".

54
00:02:42.730 --> 00:02:45.680
Which is the same thing as saying, "this place needs to be

