Or we would like something or we need something.

93
00:04:32.510 --> 00:04:35.120
It's just another way of saying those four things, which in this

94
00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:38.200
context, they're all essentially the same thing.

95
00:04:38.500 --> 00:04:40.750
Right? All of those phrases are completely fine.

96
00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:43.030
You know? Like, a drink would be nice.

97
00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.670
A drink would be useful.

98
00:04:45.290 --> 00:04:47.480
I would like a drink or I need a drink.

99
00:04:47.800 --> 00:04:50.110
Right? All of those are fine. I'm just teaching you another way of

